Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.50,0:00:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨著時代的演進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.30,0:00:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,困難的案件也與日俱增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.10,0:00:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天故事的背景是在山莊別墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.70,0:00:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謎般的繃帶怪人究竟是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.20,0:00:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.40,0:00:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.20,0:01:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山莊繃帶怪人殺人事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.00,0:01:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.60,0:01:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得那棟別墅應該是在這一帶沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個該不會是走錯路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.40,0:01:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.20,0:01:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是繞到別條路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.60,0:01:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八成是迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.70,0:02:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.90,0:02:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 柯南 就是那邊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.90,0:02:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊好像有個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.90,0:02:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是不是也要到那棟別墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.90,0:02:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人也要到別墅去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.10,0:02:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.70,0:02:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼慢 你們到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.90,0:02:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.70,0:02:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易可以招待妳到我們家別墅來玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是遲到 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他果然還是跟來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南你怎麼也不會覺得不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.70,0:02:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還用不著妳來教訓我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.40,0:02:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶著這麼一個小鬼妳根本就不能談戀愛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.40,0:02:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,談戀愛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.70,0:02:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.80,0:02:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們今天就是為了認識不錯的男孩子才來這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.90,0:02:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後我們在這裡可以跟他們在大自然的圍繞下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.20,0:02:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,談一場羅曼蒂克的戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.00,0:03:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個女人打的是這個主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.50,0:03:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼妳說的那些不錯的男孩子都還沒有來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.90,0:03:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.30,0:03:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老姐的那些朋友早就已經到這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在他們都在自己的房裡休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.80,0:03:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.10,0:03:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們這些人裡面有沒有誰頭上綁著繃帶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.00,0:03:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繃帶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.10,0:03:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天來的人沒有什麼人受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.80,0:03:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是剛才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許是住在這附近的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.00,0:03:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 別說些莫名其妙的話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.90,0:03:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點去把你們的行李放好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭和柯南的房間在二樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.60,0:03:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二樓這裡不是有很多房間嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.70,0:03:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的房間到底是哪一間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的房間應該是在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我弄錯房間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.40,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.60,0:04:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.40,0:04:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開門之前妳就不能先敲敲門嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來大家都是同一個社團的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.10,0:04:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.20,0:04:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是我老姐大學電影社的社員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們這五個人感情特別好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以每兩年都會聚會一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從蘭的旁邊開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.30,0:04:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是擔任主要工作的太田大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.50,0:04:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他旁邊的是專門負責攝影的角谷大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著是負責大道具的高橋大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.20,0:04:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 剛才失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.50,0:04:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.20,0:04:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.90,0:04:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.50,0:04:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 接下來就是負責演員化妝和服裝工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.50,0:04:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時目前在物色結婚人選的我老姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.20,0:04:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後這一位是導演兼劇本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.80,0:05:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時又是他們電影社的社長池田知佳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.10,0:05:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳該不會就是電視正在上映
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.10,0:05:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那部《青色王國》的池田知佳子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.80,0:05:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.80,0:05:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那的確是她在學生時代的作品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.30,0:05:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在終於有機會可以公諸於世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去的事別提了好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.90,0:05:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說妳馬上又要編寫下一部電影了是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.10,0:05:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼池田大師 請對妳的粉絲說幾句話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別諷刺我好嗎 角谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.30,0:05:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,角谷 你對攝影的愛好還不是一樣沒有變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我就是這個還沒放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.20,0:05:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 高橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最近是不是又胖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快要一百公斤了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鏡頭都快塞不下你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.20,0:05:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.70,0:05:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和大家聚在一起又讓人想到以前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.40,0:05:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 還有敦子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敦子要是沒有發生那件事的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也會在這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敦子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再提敦子了行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知佳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易從百忙之中抽空到這裡來散心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想談一個兩年前就已經死掉的人的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.20,0:06:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人出了名說話的口氣也不一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.70,0:06:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了…你們兩個都別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.70,0:06:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就去弄晚飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你們就先休息一下好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.60,0:06:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到外面去把那個壞掉的屋頂修理一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒好像就要下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.60,0:06:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了 高橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.20,0:06:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.40,0:06:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種工作的確只有負責道具的高橋能夠做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.20,0:06:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們其他的人就來玩撲克牌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.90,0:06:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳上哪兒去 知佳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.70,0:06:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到外面去散個步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 知佳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.40,0:06:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高橋剛才不是說傍晚會下雨嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.00,0:06:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知佳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.50,0:07:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.40,0:07:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下子沒有辦法欣賞漂亮的楓葉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.60,0:07:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得他看起來怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來帥氣中帶了些冷酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.30,0:07:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡這型的男人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.80,0:07:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.60,0:07:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳早就已經有妳的新一了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有跟妳一起來這裡真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰要他那種人來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.40,0:07:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要是在這裡我就狠狠揍他一拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.40,0:07:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就在這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.40,0:07:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起到外面散散步好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.40,0:07:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常樂意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.80,0:07:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正妳也沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.50,0:07:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是外面現在正在下雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.40,0:07:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在雨中散步也很不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.80,0:07:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.50,0:07:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明就已經有了新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣我就要誘拐新一了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有喜歡的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.60,0:08:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳不是說那個傢伙不知道什麼時候才會回來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種無情的傢伙理他幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.30,0:08:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我勸妳還是另外找個男朋友算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.30,0:08:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要讓我來教教妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.90,0:08:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼才叫做成人的戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.90,0:08:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.70,0:08:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打雷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個雷打得還真近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.70,0:08:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 蘭他們不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.70,0:09:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.30,0:09:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.30,0:09:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會走到這邊來了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太田先生你在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.90,0:09:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果在附近就回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太田…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.00,0:09:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫那麼大聲幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.10,0:09:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛…剛才那個人是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繃帶怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.30,0:09:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的 就是他在樹林裡攻擊蘭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.40,0:09:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太田大哥 你們沒有看見嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.50,0:09:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們三個人不是都在樹林裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.40,0:10:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有看見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.90,0:10:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在樹林裡面找蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有看見這麼個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.90,0:10:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們根本也沒看見 知佳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.10,0:10:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼我們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.30,0:10:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道你跑哪兒去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.00,0:10:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是因為看快要下雨了回來拿傘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.50,0:10:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是害怕打雷躲起來了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.90,0:10:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知佳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.90,0:10:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了…你們都別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個差不多也完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.90,0:10:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老姐你有沒有看到那個男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才看他往別墅這邊跑來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.70,0:10:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.00,0:10:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢 高橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.70,0:10:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才一直在上面修理屋頂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.00,0:10:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是沒有看到什麼包繃帶的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.60,0:10:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我在來別墅的吊橋上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.00,0:10:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確看到一個裝扮非常奇怪行跡詭異的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的臉我沒有看清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是披著一個黑斗篷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.60,0:10:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭上戴著一頂鬱金香形狀的黑帽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.10,0:10:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是他沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.10,0:10:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊我的人就是你在吊橋上看到那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.80,0:10:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.50,0:11:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的那個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.50,0:11:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在剛才到別墅的時候也看到過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.90,0:11:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.90,0:11:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我還以為是住在這個附近的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.50,0:11:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這附近除了過吊橋之後再往前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有兩三家獨棟的別墅之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山谷這邊要爬過山才會有人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那個男人到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看我們還是先去報警吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.60,0:11:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 妳說電話打不通?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.70,0:11:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.40,0:11:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白天明明還能打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.70,0:11:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是剛才那個雷把電話線給打斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.70,0:11:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那個綁繃帶的男人他切斷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.40,0:11:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.60,0:11:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.00,0:11:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.50,0:11:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.70,0:11:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吊橋…吊橋掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.40,0:12:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.60,0:12:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吊橋掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.80,0:12:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是它自己掉下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.20,0:12:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它本來就很舊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.70,0:12:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個吊橋是被人切斷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.80,0:12:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們自己看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.10,0:12:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綁吊橋繩子的這根柱子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都破破爛爛的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.80,0:12:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確是有人用刀割斷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.70,0:12:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是誰會做出這種事情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一定也是他做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.30,0:12:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有完沒完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼繃帶怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.00,0:12:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直一派胡言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.50,0:12:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在樹林裡攻擊蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.30,0:12:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把電話線給剪掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.60,0:12:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把吊橋砍掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.00,0:12:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都只是為了嚇唬我們罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這群人要是這樣子就害怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就正中他的下懷了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.30,0:12:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知佳子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.40,0:12:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正今天天色已經暗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.30,0:12:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家只有等到明天早上天亮以後再下山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.40,0:12:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你們剛才討論的不可開交的那個繃帶怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還會潛伏到屋裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.30,0:13:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.50,0:13:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…我先去休息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.70,0:13:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有點累了 晚飯我不吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.00,0:13:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知佳子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.90,0:13:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起 蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要讓妳幫我的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.80,0:13:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 我平常在家裡也做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.60,0:13:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場同學會辦得真是掃興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像大家都板著一張臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.50,0:13:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話要說回來都怪老姐妳提那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是指敦子的事情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.00,0:13:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.60,0:13:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個兩年前死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.90,0:13:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.80,0:13:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敦子她是在兩年以前自殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候她也是我們電影社的一員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.40,0:14:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是有一天她突然上吊死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從此之後我們就再也沒見過面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.20,0:14:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來大家感情都很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我就是覺得這麼久我們也該見見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.90,0:14:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才會主動打電話給大家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.70,0:14:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就別再提這件事情了好不好 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.20,0:14:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.90,0:14:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知佳子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.20,0:14:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她累了就先回房去休息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.60,0:14:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高橋 晚飯已經準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.70,0:14:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屋頂修理好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大致修好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 你們笑一個吧 來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.10,0:14:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高橋 你就快點下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菜都快要涼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.30,0:14:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.80,0:14:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.80,0:14:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.80,0:14:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面的窗戶旁邊好像有什麼人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.70,0:14:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶的旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.80,0:14:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知佳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.30,0:15:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 天色這麼黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不知道到哪兒去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.90,0:15:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我們也跟著那個小鬼走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們女孩子把鑰匙鎖上等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.70,0:15:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高橋 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.20,0:15:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.90,0:15:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.70,0:15:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這是知佳子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有隻手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.30,0:15:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.90,0:15:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家分散開來找找看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.20,0:15:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知佳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.30,0:15:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知佳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.40,0:15:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知佳子 妳在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.40,0:15:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知佳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.20,0:15:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知佳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作點 知佳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.70,0:16:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你說知佳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...她被人殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們到的時候她就已經被人殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.20,0:16:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經先用我的衣服把她的遺體給蓋住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知佳子怎麼會發生這種事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.00,0:16:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這全都是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.10,0:16:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都怪我計畫這次的同學會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這全都要怪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說 綾子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是妳的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.10,0:16:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯的是那個綁繃帶的怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把知佳子從我們的眼前給帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.40,0:16:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個殺人魔王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.10,0:16:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他再來攻擊的話怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.50,0:16:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要把門窗關好就沒有問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.50,0:16:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫知佳子那麼晚了還到外面閒逛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.80,0:16:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家把這件事都忘了 早點睡覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.90,0:16:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太田 你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對 現在已經很晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.00,0:17:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家再確認一下門戶就去睡覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.60,0:17:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天天一亮我們就下山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.20,0:17:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這件事原原本本的告訴警方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.80,0:17:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.70,0:17:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這些玄關沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.50,0:17:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來就只剩下我們的房間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.70,0:17:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.40,0:17:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.70,0:17:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知佳子姐姐的拖鞋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.50,0:17:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拖鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.10,0:17:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知佳子姐姐如果從玄關出去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拖鞋應該在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.70,0:17:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說知佳子姐姐不是從這裡出去的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.70,0:17:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說那個男的是進入別墅以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才把在二樓睡覺的知佳子帶走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.90,0:17:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能 園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.10,0:17:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想 柯南跟他們男孩子出去追他的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.10,0:17:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟妳還有綾子姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.30,0:17:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已經把門窗確認過一次了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.30,0:17:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而知佳子的房間那個時候也並沒有被破壞的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.50,0:17:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,窗子也都從裡面被鎖得好好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.00,0:17:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.10,0:18:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知佳子姐姐一定出去過才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為知佳子姐姐的腳上明明穿了鞋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.50,0:18:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是被殺了而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.20,0:18:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.50,0:18:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這棟別墅有沒有別的出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.30,0:18:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後面還有一個後門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.80,0:18:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.90,0:18:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是後門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.80,0:18:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.70,0:18:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這雙拖鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個絕對錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.40,0:18:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是知佳子的拖鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.50,0:18:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛好拿出符合人數的拖鞋而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.40,0:18:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說知佳子是從後門出去的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.80,0:18:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.80,0:18:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她為什麼不從玄關出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.60,0:18:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要特別從後門出去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.80,0:18:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是故意要避人耳目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊沾了好多泥巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.80,0:18:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有誰用過這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.90,0:18:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是我姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦斯的開關就在後門這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.80,0:18:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 既然拖鞋找到了我們早點睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這樣子我們的房間也沒問題了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.90,0:19:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.30,0:19:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是跟你說叫你不要擔心了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個繃帶怪人再來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.20,0:19:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你蘭姐姐我用單手也能對付他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.50,0:19:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得真好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.00,0:19:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在樹林被攻擊的時候不是嚇軟了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.70,0:19:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那個人為什麼要攻擊蘭姐姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.30,0:19:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許他看到什麼人都會攻擊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.00,0:19:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會有什麼人在恨妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.00,0:19:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好比說在空手道比賽中打成重傷的人什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.60,0:19:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這種人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了…快點睡覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.40,0:19:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過實在太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.90,0:19:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個繃帶怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.00,0:19:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上既然會從後門那邊攻擊知佳子的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.80,0:19:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還要特別繞到玄關那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們看到他的樣子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.50,0:20:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是單純為了要讓我們害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.70,0:20:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是為了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.40,0:20:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不要問那麼多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.60,0:20:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是妳害怕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.30,0:20:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不要問了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.30,0:20:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.30,0:20:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我想到哪兒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.70,0:20:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說那個繃帶怪人他是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是因為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.90,0:20:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.90,0:20:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法思考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正對方是一個身份不明的殺人魔王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.60,0:20:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是警方的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.20,0:20:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本用不著我出場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.00,0:22:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙又來攻擊蘭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.70,0:22:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快起來 蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.90,0:22:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.60,0:22:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.50,0:22:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.00,0:22:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 腳扭到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.90,0:22:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼在這個時候叫不醒...有沒有什麼東西...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.60,0:23:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.50,0:23:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用蝴蝶結變聲機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.20,0:23:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把音量提升到最大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.80,0:23:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.60,0:23:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.40,0:23:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.40,0:23:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.70,0:23:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快開門啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.80,0:23:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.60,0:23:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.10,0:23:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.70,0:23:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.90,0:23:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.20,0:23:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.90,0:23:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他為什麼要攻擊蘭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.50,0:23:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繃帶怪人果然是以蘭為目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.40,0:23:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼要攻擊蘭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.70,0:23:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像想起了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.00,0:23:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳一定要想起來 蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.40,0:24:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.90,0:24:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺死知佳子的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.00,0:24:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.40,0:24:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山莊繃帶怪人殺人事件(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.30,0:24:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.50,0:24:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.80,0:24:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.40,0:24:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看見繃帶下面的東西哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.90,0:24:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是劃傷
